data.description: **Welcome to your charming Home in Morada at Vista Del Lago **Behind the Guard Gated Community **This cozy and well-maintained property features 1 Bedroom and 1 Bathroom, making it the perfect retreat for individuals or couples seeking a comfortable and stylish living space **Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior, where natural light floods the open living area, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere *The functional kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, providing convenience for your culinary adventures *The spacious Bedroom offers a peaceful haven for rest and relaxation *Ample closet space to meet your storage needs *Well-appointed Bathroom complements the Home's overall aesthetic and ensures comfort *Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry and relish in the added privacy of being in a top-floor unit **The community amenities include Pool, Spa, Gym, Tennis & Basketball court, Clubhouse, business center and more! **Situated in a desirable location, this property provides easy access to 15 fwy, Lake, parks, Dog park, Dining, Shopping, Entertainment and etc. *Embrace the San Diego lifestyle with nearby recreational opportunities and a vibrant local community.  ***Don't miss the chance to make this delightful property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and convenience of living at Morada at Vista Del Lago
